## âš™ï¸ Installation

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone <repository-url>
cd "Fake news detection"

# 2. (Optional) Create a virtual environment
python -m venv myenv
source myenv/bin/activate  # or .\myenv\Scripts\activate (Windows)

# 3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

